from Satan. Whoever sees something he dislikes, let him blow to his left side three times and seek refuge from Satan. Verily, it will not harm him\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15126,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/19\/dua-entering-bathroom\/","url_meta":{"origin":2810,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Seek refuge before using the lavatory","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 19, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: When the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, entered the washroom, he would say, \u201cO Allah, I seek refuge in You from foul and noxious things.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 142, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 375 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6235,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/12\/satan-devil-comes-doubts\/","url_meta":{"origin":2810,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Satan: Devil will come with doubts, seek refuge in Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 12, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSatan will come to one of you and he will say, 'Who created this and that?' until he says to him, 'Who created your Lord?' When it comes to this, let him seek refuge in Allah\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2799,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/06\/isa-maryam-shaytan-birth\/","url_meta":{"origin":2810,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Jesus: Every person is touched by Satan upon birth","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 6, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo person is born but that he is pricked by Satan and he cries from\u00a0the touch of Satan, except for the son of Mary and his mother.\u201d Abu Huraira said, \"Recite the verse if you wish:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3958,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/01\/tawakkul-dua-trust-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":2810,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Tawakkul: I submit to You, I trust in You","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 1, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would\u00a0say, \u201cO Allah, I have surrendered to You and I have faith in You. I trust in You and I have turned to You. I have contested my opponents for Your sake. O Allah, I seek refuge\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u